            <h1>Mediterranean Chickpea Salad</h1>
            <p>Savor the Mediterranean sun with this vibrant salad! Nutrient-packed chickpeas, crisp cucumbers, juicy cherry tomatoes, tangy Kalamata olives, and savory feta cheese dance together in a zesty olive oil and lemon dressing, creating a refreshing and satisfying dish that's as healthy as it is delicious! </p>
            <p>Don't have a green thumb? Never fear! </p>
    
            <ul>
                <li>🍽 Serves: 4</li>
                <li>⏱ Prep Time: 15 minutes</li>
                <li>👨‍🍳 Cook Time: 0 minutes</li>
                <li>🍝 Total Time: 15 minutes</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Nutrition Facts </strong>(per serving)</li>
                <li><strong>354</strong> Calories</li>
                <li><strong>23 g</strong>  Fat</li>
                <li><strong>25 g</strong> Carbs</li>
                <li><strong>14 g</strong> Protein</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    
        <div>
            <figure>
                <img src="/images/Mediterranean-Chickpea-Salad.jpg"/>
            </figure>
            
        </div>
    
        <div></div>
